title: Paper.li Is Shutting Down
text:
Dear user,

We are writing to inform you that we will discontinue Paper.li on April 20, 2023.

This decision was not easy, but after 13 years of providing our service, it is time to say goodbye.

As a valued community member, we want to express our deepest gratitude for your support and loyalty over the years. It has been an incredible journey together, and we are honored to have had the opportunity to serve you.

After April 20, 2023, papers will no longer be accessible, and all data will be permanently deleted.

Thank you for being a part of the Paper.li community. We wish you all the best in your future endeavors!

Sincerely,

The Paper.li Team
